    <item>
      <title>里夫斯因寻求 400 亿英镑预算而面临内阁不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/reeves-faces-cabinet-unease-in-search-of-40-billion-for-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 面临内阁对削减开支规模的日益不安，她希望通过削减开支筹集 400 亿英镑（523 亿美元）来稳定英国的公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/reeves-faces-cabinet-unease-in-search-of-40-billion-for-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 18:09:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告以色列必须改善对加沙的援助才能继续获得武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/us-warns-israel-must-improve-gaza-aid-to-keep-getting-us-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府警告以色列，必须在30天内改善加沙地带“日益严峻”的人道主义危机，这意味着如果局势没有改善，美国可能会被迫依法切断美国武器的流动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/us-warns-israel-must-improve-gaza-aid-to-keep-getting-us-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 17:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称关税带来的增长将超过预计的赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-defends-economic-agenda-saying-tariffs-will-fuel-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普为其通过大幅提高关税和与美联储进行更直接磋商来改革美国经济的计划进行辩护，他认为，尽管有人预测他的议程将加剧通货膨胀并使国家债务飙升，但他的政策将带来大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/trump-defends-economic-agenda-saying-tariffs-will-fuel-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若特朗普宣布加征关税，欧盟将制定针对美国的贸易目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/eu-readies-us-trade-targets-if-election-brings-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果前总统唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选并履行其对欧盟采取惩罚性贸易措施的威胁，欧盟将列出可能加征关税的美国商品清单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/eu-readies-us-trade-targets-if-election-brings-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 16:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
